qtmir (0.7.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium


 -- Ratchanan Srirattanamet <ratchanan@ubports.com>  Tue, 23 Mar 2021 22:47:49 +0700

qtmir (0.6.1-0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Upstream-provided Debian package for qtmir.
    See upstream ChangeLog for recent changes.

 -- UBports Team <developers@ubports.com>  Mon, 28 Sep 2020 10:08:12 +0200

qtmir (0.6.0ubuntu5) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Merge Multiscreen branch

  [ Nick Dedekind ]
  * Introduced QtMir API
  * Support for multiple compositors per MirSurface
  * Support multiple screen windows & cursors with qml instantiation
  * Screen configuration API & implementation
  * Removed Unity.Screens
  * Support for workspaces

 -- Marius Gripsgard <marius@ubports.com>  Tue, 02 Jul 2019 01:36:30 +0200

qtmir (0.5.3+ubports1) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Import to ubports 

 -- Marius Gripsgard <marius@ubports.com>  Thu, 28 Dec 2017 04:30:55 +0100

